headline: DA Davidson Cuts KeyCorp (KEY) Price Target, Keeps Buy Rating
summary: KeyCorp (NYSE:KEY) is one of the 11 Dirt Cheap Stocks to Buy According to Analysts. On October 17, DA Davidson slightly reduced its price target on KeyCorp (NYSE:KEY) from $22 to $21 and kept a Buy rating.
